---
// This is the "Astro" part where we define our data
const title = "Global AI Hub";
---

<style lang="scss">
  $primary: #00ffcc; // A bright, techy neon green
  $bg: #121212; // Professional dark background

  body {
    background: $bg;
    color: white;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    padding: 40px;
  }

  .card-container {
    border: 1px solid $primary;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px $primary;
  }
</style>

<main>
  <h1>{title}</h1>
  <p>Helping the world find the right AI systems.</p>

  <div class="card-container" lang="md">
    ### 🚀 Featured AI Systems
    - **ChatGPT:** Best for writing and coding.
    - **Midjourney:** Best for high-end digital art.
    - **Astro:** The "Polyglot" tool we are using right now!
    - **ElevenLabs:** Best for realistic AI voices.
  </div>
</main>
